<ab facs="#facs_243_r1l36">Hofman darcʒu halte / daʒ Er den <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>b<ex>ur</ex>gers</expan> <expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan>
